### Associate character with a book
POST {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{characterId}}/books
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "bookId": "{{bookId}}"
}

### Remove character from a book
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/characters/{{characterId}}/books/{{bookId}}

### Delete a Character
# Replace with actual UUID
